thread.title: The Bear Services
thread.title_full: CustomUSB reviewed by The Bear Services

author: The Bear Services
title: The Bear Services
text: I am very happy with CustomUSB. All other USB drive providers had minimum quantities that were more than I needed or could afford. CustomUSB offered me a quantity I could afford. They looked at my logo as it would print on the USB drive and they made an excellent suggestion for modifying the logo for the USB drive I chose. I received the USB drives as expected, when expected. I will use CustomUSB again.
